OL,3,CNew evidence in DCI John Caldwell
OL,4,Cattempted murder trial
OL,6,FA judge has queried why "significant"
OL,7,Fnew evidence has emerged in the John
OL,8,FCaldwell attempted murder trial -
OL,9,Fthree years after he was shot.
OL,11,FThe CCTV footage being presented to
OL,12,Fthe court will impact on the ongoing
OL,13,Fdelay which has been raised as a major
OL,14,Fissue by defence lawyers on numerous
OL,15,Foccasions.
OL,17,FSeven men are charged with attempting
OL,18,Fto murder DCI Caldwell who was shot on
OL,19,FFebruary 22, 2023, while he coached a
OL,20,Ffootball team at the Omagh Youth Sport
OL,21,FCentre.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
