PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1784761381
OL,3,CNew evidence in DCI John Caldwell
OL,4,Cattempted murder trial
OL,6,FThree others are accused of preparing
OL,7,Ffor acts of terrorism.
OL,9,FFollowing the attack the assailants
OL,10,Ffled in a blue Ford Fiesta which was
OL,11,Flater found burnt out.
OL,13,FThey then switched to a black Mercedes
OL,14,Fand drove to Deverney Park in the town
OL,15,Fwhere they went to the rear of a house
OL,16,Fthen left in a white van. The weapons
OL,17,Fused in the attack remain have never
OL,18,Fbeen found.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
