PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1784761381
OL,3,CNew evidence in DCI John Caldwell
OL,4,Cattempted murder trial
OL,6,FIt is also believed there was an
OL,7,Fattempted attack two weeks beforehand
OL,8,Fwhich was stood down.
OL,10,FDefence lawyers have repeatedly
OL,11,Fexpressed frustration over the delay,
OL,12,Fwith numerous dates since last year
OL,13,Fprovided for the serving of case
OL,14,Fpapers, but these are repeatedly being
OL,15,Fpushed back.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
