FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1784761381
OL,3,CNew evidence in DCI John Caldwell
OL,4,Cattempted murder trial
OL,6,FLast month Omagh Magistrates Court was
OL,7,Ftold of a target date at the end of
OL,8,FAugust but on return today a
OL,9,Fprosecution lawyer advised of further
OL,10,Fdelay because of the discovery of new
OL,11,Fevidence.
OL,13,FShe explained: "CCTV evidence has been
OL,14,Fdiscovered that is highly relevant to
OL,15,Fthe prosecution case. Police presented
OL,16,Fthis to the (PPS) Directing officer on
OL,17,FJune 30 and July 10. Contemporaneous
OL,18,FCCTV was obtained at the beginning of
OL,19,Fthe investigation and as that
OL,20,Fprogressed additional CCTV for earlier
OL,21,Fdates was seized.
OL,26,@uD@POUxD@MpmxD@Qpn
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
