FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1784761381
OL,3,CNew evidence in DCI John Caldwell
OL,4,Cattempted murder trial
OL,6,F"Once the investigation began it was
OL,7,Frealised this wasn't an isolated date
OL,8,Fand significant planning and
OL,9,Fpreparation had been undertaken on
OL,10,Fboth the night of the attack and the
OL,11,Fearly failed attempt."
OL,26,@sD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
