FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1784761381
OL,3,CNew evidence in DCI John Caldwell
OL,4,Cattempted murder trial
OL,6,FThe court was told: "The significance
OL,7,Fof this was not apparent at the last
OL,8,Fsitting. It consists of 14 hard drives
OL,9,Fand eight USB drives and this footage
OL,10,Fis being worked on. Given the
OL,11,Fsignificance of what has been found on
OL,12,FCCTV from 10 February 2023, it is
OL,13,Fnecessary to include it in the case.
OL,14,FIt is regrettable there has been
OL,15,Fslippage, but this new evidence is
OL,16,Fimportant."
OL,18,FDistrict Judge Conor Heaney said:
OL,19,F"What confidence can this court be
OL,20,Fexpected to have in relation to the
OL,21,Ftimelines?"
OL,26,@xD@KO]{D@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
