FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1784761381
OL,3,CNew evidence in DCI John Caldwell
OL,4,Cattempted murder trial
OL,6,FThe prosecution replied: "The case was
OL,7,Fprogressing by the last update, but
OL,8,Fnobody realised the significance of
OL,9,Fwhat the police would then tell the
OL,10,FDirecting Officer. It's necessary to
OL,11,Fprove an aspect of the case."
OL,13,FThe judge asked: "What happened
OL,14,Fbetween February 2023 and June this
OL,15,Fyear?"
OL,26,@nD@ZOUsD@]O]uD@ROUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
