PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1784761381
OL,3,CNew evidence in DCI John Caldwell
OL,4,Cattempted murder trial
OL,6,FThe prosecution said: "That's the
OL,7,Fnature of this case. For every string
OL,8,Fthat is pulled, it continues to
OL,9,Funravel. Every string has to be
OL,10,Ffollowed. It just so happened this
OL,11,F(evidence) is so substantial and
OL,12,Fsignificant that it makes sense to be
OL,13,Fincluded."
OL,26,@nD@WOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
