FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1784761381
OL,3,CNew evidence in DCI John Caldwell
OL,4,Cattempted murder trial
OL,6,FBut Judge Heaney remarked: "This
OL,7,Ftroubles me. I accept there is
OL,8,Fsignificant complexity, but delay
OL,9,Fcannot be good in the administration
OL,10,Fof justice. This again throws into
OL,11,Fdoubt what the court has been told. I
OL,12,Fdon't understand why this evidence was
OL,13,Fonly recently presented and I don't
OL,14,Fknow how long it was in the possession
OL,15,Fof police. It suggests to me there was
OL,16,Fevidence which was glaringly apparent
OL,17,Fbut wasn't picked up."
OL,19,FThe precaution confirmed police would
OL,20,Fbe spoken to on this "to assuage the
OL,21,Fcourt's concerns".
OL,26,@nD@\OUyD@VO]|D@VOU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
