FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1784761381
OL,3,CNew evidence in DCI John Caldwell
OL,4,Cattempted murder trial
OL,6,FAgreeing to an adjournment until
OL,7,FAugust 18 Judge Heaney said: "This is
OL,8,Fvery unsatisfactory. It will soon be
OL,9,Fnigh on four years since the incident.
OL,10,FThe prosecution will have to reach the
OL,11,Fpoint where they simply say what we
OL,12,Fhave, we have. Any other material will
OL,13,Fhave to be served as additional
OL,14,Fevidence."
